  "code": "---\nconfig:\n  theme: redux-color\n  look: neo\n---\n\nsequenceDiagram\n        actor User as User\n        participant WebUI as WebUI\n        participant Server as Server\n        participant Database as Database\n        User->>+ WebUI: 1. Log out\n        WebUI ->>+ Server: 2. POST / logout{}\n        Server ->> +Database : 3. Destroy user session and token invalidation\n        Database -->>- Server: 4. Acknowledge session termination\n        Server -->>- WebUI : 5. 200 / {meta, message}\n        WebUI -->>- User: 6. Redirect to login page\n        opt Logout failed\n            WebUI ->>+ Server: 2. POST / logout{}\n            Server->> +Database : 3. Attempt to terminate user session\n            Database -->>- Server: 4. Return failure / timeout\n            Server -->>- WebUI : 5. 500 / {message}\n            WebUI -->> User: 6. Display error message\n        end",
