    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个用户登出流程的时序图，从User点击退出开始，经过WebUI、Server到Database，最后返回登录页。另外还要考虑登出失败的情况，用opt片段表示。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "WebUI",
        "Server",
        "Database",
        "opt"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，四个参与者：User作为actor，WebUI、Server、Database作为participant。主流程是正常登出，opt分支处理失败场景。请问正常流程里Database要做什么具体操作？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "WebUI",
        "Server",
        "Database"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "正常流程：Database收到请求后要销毁用户session，同时做token invalidation，然后返回确认消息给Server。Server回200状态码，WebUI最后把用户重定向到登录页。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Database",
        "Server",
        "WebUI",
        "destroy user session",
        "token invalidation",
        "acknowledge",
        "redirect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，主流程六步已经画好：User发起logout，WebUI POST到Server，Server调用Database销毁session和token，Database返回acknowledge，Server回200，WebUI redirect到login page。现在处理opt分支，失败场景怎么触发？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "WebUI",
        "Server",
        "Database",
        "POST /logout",
        "200",
        "redirect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "opt条件写\"Logout failed\"。失败时Database尝试terminate session但返回failure或timeout，Server回500，WebUI直接display error message给用户，不走redirect。",
      "elements_involved": [
