      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：opt分支里WebUI也是先发POST /logout到Server，Server再调Database，但Database返回的是failure或timeout，然后Server回500，WebUI显示错误信息。对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WebUI",
